And more

1194
01:48:42,439 --> 01:48:45,901
After your boots dry

1195
01:48:45,943 --> 01:48:47,778
And the tobacco's

1196
01:48:47,820 --> 01:48:51,490
All but gone

1197
01:48:51,532 --> 01:48:55,869
Along with all those postcards

1198
01:48:55,911 --> 01:48:57,996
You've carried

1199
01:48:58,038 --> 01:49:00,999
Under your arm

1200
01:49:01,041 --> 01:49:05,379
After I remember

1201
01:49:05,420 --> 01:49:09,466
All the words I couldn't say

1202
01:49:10,509 --> 01:49:14,346
And after this long night

1203
01:49:14,388 --> 01:49:16,974
Fades away

1204
01:49:19,601 --> 01:49:23,480
I will love you

1205
01:49:25,816 --> 01:49:28,944
After the war

1206
01:49:28,986 --> 01:49:31,655
I love you

1207
01:49:31,697 --> 01:49:34,658
For always

1208
01:49:34,700 --> 01:49:37,244
Forever more

1209
01:49:39,121 --> 01:49:42,833
I will love you

1210
01:49:44,877 --> 01:49:48,380
After the war

1211
01:49:48,422 --> 01:49:50,340
Forever

1212
01:49:50,382 --> 01:49:52,968
For always

1213
01:49:53,010 --> 01:49:56,013
And more

1214
01:50:02,728 --> 01:50:06,523
After this blackbird

1215
01:50:06,565 --> 01:50:08,358
Lifts up

1216
01:50:08,400 --> 01:50:10,903
From off your chest

1217
01:50:12,154 --> 01:50:15,824
And after your soul

1218
01:50:15,866 --> 01:50:20,871
Takes its final rest

1219
01:50:21,497 --> 01:50:25,334
My love, I forgive you

1220
01:50:26,835 --> 01:50:31,089
You never planned to die

1221
01:50:31,131 --> 01:50:35,385
And love,
I'll place two pennies

1222
01:50:35,427 --> 01:50:37,596
Over your eyes

1223
01:50:43,352 --> 01:50:46,814
I will love you

